        Miller Pink they are colour, the alpha state, and the moments before and after sport.</p>

      <p>As we catalogue the component parts of every concept over the next decade, we'll not only be able to map the
        pathways to successful innovation, but also reveal ground-breaking combinations still waiting to be
        explored.</p>
